{"tid":2273763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓：促金將軍冷靜 提醒世人北韓曾在奧巴馬政府核試","createTime":"2020-11-06T03:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T07:10:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d0ee8d95e4b421363278bb50c679d2104f27565c","tid":2273763,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:27:45.000Z","msg":"南韓促北韓不要試圖測試美國新政府加劇緊張局勢 <br />\n<br />\n南韓統一部長李仁榮敦促北韓，不論美國總統大選結果如何，都要遵守並執行與美國和南韓達成的協議，不要試圖測試新一屆美國政府。他又重提北韓曾於美國前總統奧巴馬上任第一年進行核試，認為在美國制定新政策前加劇朝鮮半島緊張局勢，並非好選擇。 <br />\n<br />\n李仁榮在首爾出席一個和平論壇時又提到，南韓及美國政府在過往換屆時改變對朝政策，為達致朝鮮半島和平帶來挑戰，強調南韓今次不論美國大選結果，都會堅定推進朝鮮半島和平進程，並會盡快向美方新政府表明立場。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2365040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2365040&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8oaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=63b42dbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2365040</a>"},{"pid":"1fc1da16eaf97a674697c891be259639788a0ea3","tid":2273763,"uid":66049,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:37:36.000Z","msg":"金仔都唔gur拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美朝關係玩完"},{"pid":"a6ffdd5bc3fed3fd416919a292069d6302a626fd","tid":2273763,"uid":266342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:43:24.000Z","msg":"人家北朝鮮做d乜關你奶支文在淫政權乜事，收皮啦"},{"pid":"4ac2b1feb76c4a1b56c38e1ce69bc6afb593de3f","tid":2273763,"uid":66242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1fc1da16eaf97a674697c891be259639788a0ea3","tid":2273763,"uid":66049,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:37:36.000Z","msg":"金仔都唔gur拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美朝關係玩完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762a667835bd266e2772f0a7ebaeb1d7df2ae5a5","tid":2273763,"uid"